<div id="pf28" class="pf w4 h26" data-page-no="28"><div class="pc pc28 w4 h26"><img class="bi x0 y0 w5 h27" alt="" src="bg28.png"/><div class="t m144 x19 h1d y438 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">RAY or the Unread] d,Peop14 Group of Nati </div><div class="t me0 xc1 h1d y5cd ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eric s in ,,he uppe Yakinia Valley of </div><div class="t m105 x7e h1d y5ce ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m197 x3e h1d y5cf ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">th </div><div class="t m3c4 x5 h1d y5d0 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ashington where no permane work </div><div class="t mce x90 h1d y5d1 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stablished. </div><div class="t m70 x2d h20 y5d2 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">blessed through them (see Gen. 12:3; Gal. 3:8) when they (the Jews) ruled </div><div class="t m4b x2d h20 y16f ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">over the nations. But Paul made it clear that the real promise to Abraham </div><div class="t m76 x3 h20 y170 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">was not a piece of land or a throne, but righteousness; and Abraham&apos;s real </div><div class="t m75 x3 h20 y5d3 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">descendants are those who have Abraham&apos;s faith, regardless of their blood </div><div class="t md6 x3 h20 y5d4 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">relationship to him. Any person, of any nation, can by faith lay claim to the </div><div class="t m280 x3 h20 y5d5 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">promise of righteousness that was first made to Abraham. This, Paul said, </div><div class="t m54 x3 h20 y213 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is how all nations were to be blessed through Abraham. </div><div class="t m79 x3 h1f y353 ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">APPLICATION TO MY LIFE: </div><div class="t m146 xb2 h20 y5d6 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m3c5 x8a h20 y172 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How important is it to my peace of mind to know that through </div><div class="t m115 xb2 h20 y5d7 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus my sins are entirely forgiven? What would life be like if I did </div><div class="t m1d5 xb2 h20 y355 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not know that? </div><div class="t m146 xb2 h20 y356 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m3c6 x8a h20 ye5 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Most Christians today are not blood descendants of Abraham. </div><div class="t m3c7 xb2 h20 y5d8 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Nevertheless, in what ways can we have a false hope of favor with </div><div class="t m239 xb2 h20 y5d9 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God as the chosen nation did in Christ&apos;s time? </div><div class="t m146 xb2 h20 y176 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m2ef x8a h20 y4e6 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How can I know whether I am truly trusting in Christ or my good </div><div class="t m88 xb2 h20 y359 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">deeds for salvation? </div><div class="t m29b x3 h1f y35c ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FURTHER STUDY AND MEDITATION: </div><div class="t m3c8 xc2 h20 y5da ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Read the chapter titled </div><div class="t m35f x3 h20 y35d ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Justified by Faith&quot; in </div><div class="t m3c9 x88 h20 y5db ff6 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Selected Messages, </div><div class="t mb0 xc3 h20 y177 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">book 1, pp. 389-398. </div><div class="t m54 x3 h1f y35f ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m3ca x50 h20 y5dc ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We can be saved only by faith in Christ, never by our </div><div class="t m3ae x3 h20 y5dd ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">works, by family ties, or by church membership. Faith in Christ brings </div><div class="t m112 x3 h20 y5de ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">both the forgiveness of sin and the power of the Holy Spirit that transforms </div><div class="t m1d5 x3 h20 y5df ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our lives. Abraham&apos;s faith in God&apos;s promises brought him the gift of right-</div><div class="t m233 x3 h20 y5e0 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eousness, and that same gift is available to every Christian who exercises </div><div class="t m17c x3 h20 y5e1 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Abraham&apos;s faith in God. Christ Himself is the Gift who comes to us by the </div><div class="t m238 x3 h20 y5e2 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Holy Spirit. </div><div class="t m3a0 x3 h1f y5e3 ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">40 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
